From: guillaume <guillaume.chaye@zeetim.com>
Subject: [PATCH] sched_daemon: retire ASUS task scheduler by default on standalone AP (nvram gtbe98_sched_daemon)

Phase 2 (rc-drain): sched_daemon is not load-bearing on a standalone AP (scheduling we
care about moves to webui/cron). Gate both the launch funnel start_sched_daemon()
(rc/services.c) and its watchdog respawn sched_daemon_check() (rc/watchdog.c) on a new
unused nvram flag gtbe98_sched_daemon (default off, 0024/0028 early-return model).

The watchdog respawn is UNGATED in stock (sched_daemon_check just re-execs on
!pids("sched_daemon")), so removing the binary without this gate would loop a failed
respawn every watchdog period. Re-enable: nvram set gtbe98_sched_daemon=1 ; nvram commit.
See gt-be98-docs/device/plans/patch-0033-0034-notes.md (br-0047/br-0048 webui slices).
---
diff --git a/release/src/router/rc/services.c b/release/src/router/rc/services.c
--- a/release/src/router/rc/services.c
+++ b/release/src/router/rc/services.c
@@ -15181,6 +15181,15 @@
 #ifdef RTCONFIG_BCM_MFG
 	return;
 #endif
+	/* Fork GT-BE98 : sched_daemon (ordonnanceur de taches ASUS : reboot/wifi sched,
+	 * led/aura, telemetrie temporisee) desactive par defaut sur AP autonome -- les
+	 * planifications utiles passent par le webui/cron. Garde placee AVANT le relais
+	 * notify_rc pour couvrir aussi le chemin PID1. Son respawn watchdog
+	 * (sched_daemon_check) est NON gate en stock, d'ou la garde jumelle ci-dessous.
+	 * Reactiver : nvram set gtbe98_sched_daemon=1 ; nvram commit. */
+	if (!nvram_get_int("gtbe98_sched_daemon"))
+		return;
+
 	if(getpid()!=1) {
 		notify_rc("start_sched_daemon");
 		return;
diff --git a/release/src/router/rc/watchdog.c b/release/src/router/rc/watchdog.c
--- a/release/src/router/rc/watchdog.c
+++ b/release/src/router/rc/watchdog.c
@@ -11107,6 +11107,13 @@
 #if defined(RTCONFIG_SCHED_DAEMON)
 static void sched_daemon_check()
 {
+	/* Fork GT-BE98 : ne pas relancer sched_daemon s'il est desactive (cf.
+	 * start_sched_daemon). Ce respawn est NON gate en stock -> sans cette garde,
+	 * retirer le binaire produirait une boucle d'echec de relance a chaque periode
+	 * de watchdog. Reactiver : nvram set gtbe98_sched_daemon=1 ; nvram commit. */
+	if (!nvram_get_int("gtbe98_sched_daemon"))
+		return;
+
 	if (!pids("sched_daemon"))
 		start_sched_daemon();
 }
